# FlowCare — System Architecture & Design Document

> **Queue & Appointment Booking System** for a multi-branch service organization operating in Oman.
> Technology: Node.js · Express · PostgreSQL

---

## 1. High-Level System Architecture

### Layered Architecture (Clean Separation of Concerns)

```
┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      Client Layer                         │
│  (Web App · Mobile App · Admin Dashboard · Third-Party)   │
└──────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────┘
                           │ HTTPS / REST
┌──────────────────────────▼────────────────────────────────┐
│                   API Gateway / Reverse Proxy              │
│              (Nginx — rate limiting, SSL, CORS)            │
└──────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────┘
                           │
┌──────────────────────────▼────────────────────────────────┐
│                  Express Application Server                │
│                                                            │
│  ┌────────────┐  ┌───────────┐  ┌───────────────────────┐ │
│  │ Middleware  │  │  Routes   │  │  Global Error Handler │ │
│  │ (Auth, RBAC│  │ /api/v1/* │  │  + Request Logger     │ │
│  │  Validate) │  │           │  │                       │ │
│  └─────┬──────┘  └─────┬─────┘  └───────────────────────┘ │
│        │               │                                   │
│  ┌─────▼───────────────▼──────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │              Service / Business Logic Layer         │   │
│  │  (BookingService, SlotService, BranchService, …)   │   │
│  └─────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────┘   │
│                        │                                   │
│  ┌─────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │             Data Access Layer (DAL / Repositories)  │   │
│  │         (Knex.js query builder — raw SQL when needed│   │
│  └─────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────┘   │
└────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────┘
                         │
┌────────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────┐
│                      PostgreSQL Database                   │
│         (Primary + optional read replica later)            │
└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

Peripheral Services:
  • File Storage   — local disk (dev) / S3-compatible (prod)
  • Logging Sink   — Winston → stdout/file → optional ELK
  • Cache (future) — Redis for session + slot locks
```

### Key Architectural Decisions

| Concern | Decision | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| **ORM / Query** | Knex.js (query builder) | Fine-grained SQL control, easy migrations |
| **Auth** | JWT (access + refresh tokens) | Stateless, scalable, standard |
| **Validation** | Joi / Zod at middleware | Fail fast, never trust client |
| **File Uploads** | Multer + S3-compatible store | Stream to storage, no memory bloat |
| **Migrations** | Knex migrations (versioned) | Reproducible, rollback-safe |
| **Seed Data** | Idempotent seed scripts | `INSERT … ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING` |
| **API Versioning** | URL prefix `/api/v1` | Future-proof breaking changes |

